    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>The 1st International Workshop on Pervasive Computing and Dialogue Systems (PerDial 2018) aims to serve as a platform for cross-disciplinary discussions on ways, problems, challenges and perspectives of mutual integration of Dialogue Systems and Pervasive Computing technologies. </p>
    <p>Dialogue Systems have been a hot topic of discussion in a research community for the last two decades. They are inalienable part of Human-Computer Interaction, and allow the integration of Artificial Intelligence systems in our everyday lives smoothly and naturally, through an easy, human-like communication. Pervasive Computing technologies can contact user at a close level as well as be insensibly integrated in environment, providing spatially distributed information.</p>
